<li>2009 Archon Award - Sigma Theta Tau International (Nursing Award)</li>
<li>2009 Austin College Leadership Award, Sherman TX - life work to take courageous stand on education issues for peace <a href="http://www.austincollege.edu/category.asp?352" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.austincollege.edu/category.asp?352" rel="nofollow">[7]</a></li>
